OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FGrenfell bereaved and survivors will
OL,8,Fgather this weekend nine years on from
OL,9,Fthe fatal fire, for what is the final
OL,10,Fanniversary before the tower block is
OL,11,Fcompletely taken down.
OL,13,FIt comes after police and prosecutors
OL,14,Fannounced last month that up to 20
OL,15,Fcompanies and 57 individuals could
OL,16,Fface criminal charges over the blaze.
OL,18,FDecisions will be made on whether any
OL,19,Fcharges will be brought before next
OL,20,Fyear's 10th anniversary, the
OL,21,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
