CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781387266
OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FOn Sunday evening, the annual silent
OL,8,Fwalk will take place in west London,
OL,9,Ffollowed by the reading of the names
OL,10,Fof the 72 dead, and speeches by
OL,11,Fcampaigners.
OL,13,FThe blaze in June 2017 was found by a
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry to have been avoidable,
OL,15,Fhaving been preceded by "decades of
OL,16,Ffailure" by governments and the
OL,17,Fbuilding industry to act on the
OL,18,Fdangers of flammable materials on high-
OL,19,Frise buildings.
OL,26,@wD@YOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781387266
OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FThe inquiry's final report in 2024
OL,8,Ffound victims, the bereaved and
OL,9,Fsurvivors were "badly failed" through
OL,10,Fincompetence, dishonesty and greed,
OL,11,Fwith the tower block covered in
OL,12,Fcombustible products because of the
OL,13,F"systematic dishonesty" of firms which
OL,14,Fmade and sold the cladding and
OL,15,Finsulation.
OL,17,FInquiry chairman Sir Martin Moore-Bick
OL,18,Fcondemned the "deliberate and
OL,19,Fsustained" manipulation of fire safety
OL,20,Ftesting, misrepresentation of test
OL,21,Fdata and misleading of the market.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@]O]uD@AOUuD@WO]zD@OOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
