OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FMr Daffarn said it is "absolutely
OL,13,Fessential" that people and companies
OL,14,Fare held to account for what happened.
OL,16,FHe said : "It's encouraging that we
OL,17,Fhave a timeline now where there is a
OL,18,Fchance of these criminal prosecutions
OL,19,Fhappening, which is absolutely
OL,20,Fessential."
OL,26,@tD@WOUuD@JO]xD@KOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
