CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781387266
OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FGrenfell United, which represents many
OL,8,Fof the bereaved and survivors, has
OL,9,Fasked people to join Sunday's walk "in
OL,10,Fsolidarity to remember those we lost,
OL,11,Fand demand justice", noting that it is
OL,12,F"the last anniversary with any part of
OL,13,FGrenfell Tower remaining".
OL,15,FMr Daffarn said: "This is the first
OL,16,Fyear that bereaved and survivors are
OL,17,Fnot going to be able to visit the
OL,18,Ftower to lay flowers and pay our
OL,19,Fcondolences.
OL,26,@qD@dOUsD@SO]tD@AOUuD@YO]wD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
