CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781387266
OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,F"We don't know exactly what the site
OL,8,Fis going to look like (next year on
OL,9,Fthe 10th anniversary), so people are
OL,10,Fhaving to find different ways to
OL,11,Fremember."
OL,13,FThe process of bringing the tower down
OL,14,Fbegan in September last year and
OL,15,FGovernment said at that point that it
OL,16,Fwas expected to take around two years
OL,17,Fto be completed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
