OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781387266
OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FNews of the Government's decision last
OL,8,Fyear was met with criticism from some
OL,9,Fbereaved and survivors who expressed
OL,10,Ftheir upset and shock, saying they
OL,11,Ffelt they had not had their views
OL,12,Fconsidered before the decision was
OL,13,Ftaken.
OL,15,FThen-housing secretary Angela Rayner
OL,16,Flater said in an interview that she
OL,17,Fknew the meeting with those most
OL,18,Fclosely affected was going to be
OL,19,F"really difficult" and that there was
OL,20,F"not a consensus" among everyone over
OL,21,Fwhat should happen to the tower.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@RO]|D@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781387266
OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FViews have varied, with her department
OL,8,Facknowledging there had been hopes
OL,9,Famong some people for some of the
OL,10,Ftower to remain in place as a memorial
OL,11,Fto what happened while others had
OL,12,Freported this would be "too painful".
OL,14,FThe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,15,Fand Local Government confirmed that
OL,16,F"as a mark of respect" work at the
OL,17,Ftower will pause from Friday until
OL,18,FTuesday.
OL,26,@tD@XOUtD@dO]xD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
