OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FSeparately, the Grenfell Tower
OL,8,FMemorial Commission has been
OL,9,Fconsulting on plans for a permanent
OL,10,Fmemorial in the area of the tower,
OL,11,Fwith recommendations including a
OL,12,F"sacred space", designed to be a
OL,13,F"peaceful place for remembering and
OL,14,Freflecting".
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@NO]uD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
