OL,3,CGrenfell remembered on final
OL,4,Canniversary before tower's complete
OL,5,Ctake down
OL,7,FDesign team Freehaus was chosen last
OL,8,Fyear to create a memorial and is
OL,9,Fworking with bereaved and survivor
OL,10,Ffamilies as well as the local
OL,11,Fcommunity to produce a final design
OL,12,Fwhich is expected to be announced in
OL,13,Fmid-2027.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/11
